deck: Explore the sexier side of the dark arts in these collections of gorgeous incantations!
description: Get out the pentagrams and light the sacred candles, it’s time to enter the ancient circle of Wicca and tap into the power of nature herself! More pretty practitioners of the dark arts in this third volume of the series, with arcane artwork by as Arantza, Pelaez, Sosa, Greco, DeSimone, Maraschi, & more. Cover painting by Pelaez.
name: A Gallery Girls Book

deck: Those buxom buccaneers are back, displaying all the cold-blooded charms they brazenly showcased in the first collection of Treasured Chests! There's just something about a semi-nude sea-faring brigand that shivers one's timbers!
description: Those buxom buccaneers are back, displaying all the cold-blooded charms they brazenly showcased in the first collection of Treasured Chests! There's just something about a semi-nude sea-faring brigand that shivers one's timbers! The scurvy lot of illustrators that have signed aboard to make this second voyage possible include: Arantza, Blas Gallego, Esteban Maroto, Rich Larson, Mitch Byrd, Mike Hoffman, J.L. Marin, Roca, and many others! Special wrap-around cover painting by Blas Gallego.
name: A Gallery Girls Collection

deck: 'Tis another journey 'cross the seven seas in search of booty! Lots of booty! Shake that booty! These pretty little pirates are luscious as they are vicious, and to underestimate them is to take your last breath! In our third journey, these ladies will put more than wind in your sails, as they scramble up your mast to find hidden treasures!
description: 'Tis another journey 'cross the seven seas in search of booty! Lots of booty! Shake that booty! name: A Gallery Girls Collection

deck: In this fourth installment of buxom brigands, we see the lasses with cutlasses shiverin' timbers and shakin' their booty for all to see!
description: In this fourth installment of buxom brigands, we see the lasses with cutlasses shiverin' timbers and shakin' their booty for all to see! High-flying adventure and very tiny pirate outfits, as illustrated by such a scurvy lot as Arantza, Mitch Byrd, Tomas Giorello, Ruben Meriggi, Alejandro Colucci, Pedro Cuevas, and many more! Cover painting by Pelaez.
name: A Gallery Girls Collection

deck: For centuries, fishermen have braved storms, sickness, and death, all for the sake of fish. C’mon, let’s get serious! They’re out for Mermaids!
description: For centuries, fishermen have braved storms, sickness, and death, all for the sake of fish. C’mon, let’s get serious! They’re out for Mermaids! We’ve found even more aquatic cuties, with art by Anibal Maraschi, Marcelo Sosa, Claudio Aboy, Arantza, Ponce, Florio, Alejandro Colucci, J.L. Czerniawski and others. Cover painting by Pelaez.
name: A Gallery Girls Collection

deck: Of all the Gallery Girls collections, perhaps the most popular is the sea-going series of the Seven Seas - Mermaids!
description: Of all the Gallery Girls collections, perhaps the most popular is the sea-going series of the Seven Seas - Mermaids! In our fourth installment of such salty goodness, we’ve enlisted the aquatic artworks of such expert fisherfolk as Pelaez, Arantza, DelRivero, Colucci, Meriggi, and a boat-load of others! Cover painting by Pelaez.

deck: Weaker sex?  Wishful thinking!  A pantheon of powerful female warriors, as illustrated by an international collection of artists.

deck: Heaven’s missing more than just one angel! We’re counting over sixty that have gone AWOL, jut to end up in this book!
description: Heaven’s missing more than just one angel! We’re counting over sixty that have gone AWOL, jut to end up in this book! Angel Lust 2 flies into the sky and bring an all-new collection of heavenly creatures down to Earth for we merest of mortals to enjoy! Art by Candia, Buci, Danilo, Flores, LeBlanc, and more. Cover painting by Pelaez.
name: A Gallery Girls Collection
